{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3431d593eb","title":"周恩来对外交部指示要点","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"82acf78cbd","index":0,"year":1968,"month":4,"day":1,"articleId":"3431d593eb","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对外关系和政策","id":"2bffb53b5b","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0785fdad49","type":"title","text":"周恩来对外交部指示要点","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3431d593eb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f5a45738b","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来对外交部指示要点","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3431d593eb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45fb5faf9e","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3431d593eb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"72ccc1b34e","type":"paragraph","text":"1968.04.01","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3431d593eb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab24ba14a7","type":"paragraph","text":"去年二月逆流牵扯到外交部就是想完全复原。二月逆流的特点是把矛头对准毛主席亲自发动的无产阶级文化大革命，对准以毛主席为首林副主席为副的无产阶级司令部，对准坚决执行无产阶级革命路线的中央文革。当时二月逆流要恢复刘少奇为代表的资产阶级司令部的旧秩序，为资本主义复辟开辟道路，进而搞资本主义复辟。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3431d593eb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9184f2cf5b","type":"paragraph","text":"翻案风有各种形式，极“左”也可以为二月逆流翻案。因为极“左”是同右合作的，是保护右的。现在反右是主要方面，要反右倾保守主义，右倾分裂主义。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3431d593eb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"628eca67d8","type":"paragraph","text":"要击退为二月逆流翻案风。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3431d593eb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2f4eeacc24","type":"paragraph","text":"现在，反右倾保守主义，反右倾分裂主义，右倾机会主义，必须防止极“左”翻案，它要翻案是不允许的。但当前主攻方向是反右。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3431d593eb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b0ae14bfe","type":"paragraph","text":"犯极“左”错误要翻案是不允许的，有人翻也不怕。什么叫右倾保守主义，就是恢复旧秩序、旧官，这是办不到的。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3431d593eb","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}